Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,VITALS. Joint blood-logistics decision support for DHA RESCUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.94,0:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,USINDOPACOM Distributed Maritime Operations — one depot, twelve\Nspokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Predicting which spoke fails first when the hub gets constrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve distributed Marine units stream onto the hub-and-spoke map.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Constrain the hub: airlift loss, typhoon CPA inside 48 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Spokes turn red one-by-one as the cascading-failure simulation runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A multi-step LLM agent scores all 12 spokes — strict JSON output.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.52,0:00:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a Kamiwaza-deployed hero model drafts the Commander's Decision\NBrief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,BLUF, top-3 spoke nodes at risk, secondary-effect cascades. One page.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitigation actions cite approved buy-on-market vendors by id.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.54,0:00:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs inside the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
